    "We compared the obtained results with a baseline built as in the previous section.",
    "As shown, GraphSage demonstrates good performance, superior to that of the pipeline tested considering higher thresholds for creating networks.",
    "The use of AI-based triage system in EDs could have significant implications for emergency medical care.",
    "Automating the triage process could reduce wait times and ensure that patients receive care proportional to the urgency of their condition.",
    "This could improve patient outcomes and operational efficiency within hospitals."
